<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
McPherson (1981) recognised two subspecies but these are poorly defined morphologically and are not recognised here. In any case this species is not always easily separable from 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Ipomoea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="wolcottiana">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Ipomoea wolcottiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
or 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Ipomoea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="populina">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">I. populina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, the former differing in the often obscurely pubescent sepals and the latter in the liana habit.
</paragraph>
